# Regex patterns for URLs lychee should skip.
# Social platforms aggressively bot-block CI runners (403/429/999),
# so excluding them keeps the link check meaningful rather than flaky.
^https?://(www\.)?linkedin\.com
^https?://(www\.)?x\.com
^https?://(www\.)?twitter\.com
^https?://(www\.)?reddit\.com
^https?://(www\.)?medium\.com
^https?://(www\.)?youtube\.com
^https?://skillicons\.dev
^https?://fonts\.(googleapis|gstatic)\.com
